OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FUnlawful trade barrier     
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fwarning over bottle scheme 
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A leading lawyer has claimed that      
OL,6, Scotland's bottle deposit return scheme
OL,7, could create an unlawful trade barrier 
OL,8, with the rest of the UK.               
OL,10,FThe initiative is due to launch in     
OL,11,FAugust and is designed to boost        
OL,12,Frecycling via a 20p deposit on         
OL,13,Fsingle-use drinks bottles and cans.    
OL,15,FBut Aidan O'Neill KC said the Scottish 
OL,16,Fgovernment may have to delay it until  
OL,17,Fthe launch of a UK-wide scheme in 2025.
OL,19,FHe made the remarks in advice sought   
OL,20,Ffrom a group of distillers.            
